{"tid":775875,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港美警民被捕率之比較","createTime":"2018-08-11T13:46:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T17:22:40.000Z","uid":170229,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9023993e2049b37da24c32a69c77cec8746f443f","tid":775875,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:46:35.000Z","msg":"據警方數字，在2016年，非文職警員數量為36534人。其中，43人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n執法人員被捕率為43/36534= 0.001177 （取四位有效數字）<br />\n<br />\n在同一文件中可見，本港於16年 每十萬人破案率為827<br />\n破案率為0.00827<br />\n<br />\nArrest ratio civilian vs cops: 7.026<br />\n即在香港，每7個平民被捕，就有一位執法人員被捕。<br />\n<br />\n對比美國<br />\n2012年，共有429925名執法人員。其中有1170人被捕。<br />\n被捕率為0.002721。<br />\n<br />\n同時，美國全國每十萬人被捕率為3888.2。<br />\n被捕率為0.03888。<br />\n<br />\nArrest ratio: 14.29。<br />\n即在美國，約每14位平民被捕，就有一位執法人員被捕。<br />\n<br />\n美國對香港民警被捕率之比例為 2.034。<br />\n即對比當地平民，香港執法人員被捕率為美國之兩倍。<br />\n<br />\n美國對香港執法人員被捕率比例為 2.312。<br />\n即對比香港，美國執法人員有兩倍的機率被捕。<br />\n<br />\n美國對香港平民被捕率為4.701；即約5個美國人被捕，就有一個香港人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n結論：<br />\n美國人與美國執法人員被捕率皆高於香港，但考慮到警方的行為亦會受當地文化和當地罪犯所影響，故以警民被捕率作比較。就其而言，美國執法人員比本港執法人員優秀一倍有餘。<br />\n<br />\n不足：<br />\n未能尋得2016年的美國執法人員被捕數字<br />\n沒有其他外國數字作比較<br />\n<br />\n此比較不過為兩三小時娛樂之作，亦不全合學術論文規格，意在拋磚引玉、引起討論。若有其他數據提供，以作更新之用，歡迎留言。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.rfi.fr/tw/政治/20180615-脫下制服就是賊香港半年至少26警察犯案被捕\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Famp.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%2F20180615-%E8%84%AB%E4%B8%8B%E5%88%B6%E6%9C%8D%E5%B0%B1%E6%98%AF%E8%B3%8A%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%8A%E5%B9%B4%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%9126%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E7%8A%AF%E6%A1%88%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95&d=Tr44wNkJylbUub81S4auEZUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=8c5c63ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/amp.rfi.fr/tw/政治/20180615-脫下制服就是賊香港半年至少26警察犯案被捕</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/police_in_figure/2017_police_in_fig.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Finfo%2Fdoc%2Fpolice_in_figure%2F2017_police_in_fig.pdf&d=Tr44wNkJylbUub81S4auEZUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=19e544a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/info/doc/police_in_figure/2017_police_in_fig.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.statista.com/statistics/191694/number-of-law-enforcement-officers-in-the-us/#0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Fstatistics%2F191694%2Fnumber-of-law-enforcement-officers-in-the-us%2F%230&d=Tr44wNkJylbUub81S4auEZUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=6dc996d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.statista.com/statistics/191694/number-of-law-enforcement-officers-in-the-us/#0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.vice.com/en_us/article/595kv3/police-crime-database\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.vice.com%2Fen_us%2Farticle%2F595kv3%2Fpolice-crime-database&d=Tr44wNkJylbUub81S4auEZUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=637e9ea5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.vice.com/en_us/article/595kv3/police-crime-database</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.statista.com/statistics/191267/arrest-rate-for-all-offenses-in-the-us-since-1990/#0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Fstatistics%2F191267%2Farrest-rate-for-all-offenses-in-the-us-since-1990%2F%230&d=Tr44wNkJylbUub81S4auEZUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=ca320b74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.statista.com/statistics/191267/arrest-rate-for-all-offenses-in-the-us-since-1990/#0</a>"},{"pid":"a281c7efddc9da49270ea3013c52fef8171ec1a0","tid":775875,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T13:58:50.000Z","msg":"美國黑警當值做閪野都會俾返差佬拉, 香港?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6fc0a08a4e37dd8869815cf317d0c8f862d5b03","tid":775875,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T14:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm